1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:40,950
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

3
00:01:40,990 --> 00:01:43,000
[Episode 22]

4
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:47,890
This tea is called Xiangyunhong.

5
00:01:48,050 --> 00:01:48,560
No need.

6
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,020
I'm not here for tea.

7
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:52,180
I just want to take a rest.

8
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,020
I'll serve you tea, Young Master.

9
00:02:05,820 --> 00:02:06,820
I didn't mean it.

10
00:02:08,820 --> 00:02:09,370
Wait.

11
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,160
It was my careless mistake.

12
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:13,300
It had nothing to do with Miss Qing'er here.

13
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:14,979
Can you not take this down?

14
00:02:14,979 --> 00:02:16,100
I'm just following the rules.

15
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:18,560
Did the girls offend you, Young Master?

16
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:22,940
The girls are fine.

17
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:24,030
I have a question

18
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:25,430
for you though, Miss Bihuang.

19
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:26,820
Go ahead please, Young Master.

20
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,260
If the girls from the Girls' Mansion

21
00:02:28,410 --> 00:02:29,410
make any mistake,

22
00:02:29,810 --> 00:02:30,650
will they be punished?

23
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,990
We are fair in meting out rewards and punishments.

24
00:02:33,329 --> 00:02:34,730
We only deduct some money from their salaries.

25
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,290
Then why are they so scared?

26
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:39,610
We are here to make money.

27
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,910
Of course we don't want our salary to be deducted.

28
00:02:42,660 --> 00:02:43,420
Even so,

29
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:45,690
may I ask you a favor, Miss Bihuang?

30
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,460
If any mistake

31
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:48,820
is made by the girls serving us today,

32
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:51,100
I'll pay for their fine. Is that okay?

33
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:54,820
This may not be...

34
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:56,250
If the girls are fearful,

35
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:57,660
the guests won't be at ease, either.

36
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,340
If you can't make this call, Miss Bihuang,

37
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,190
I'll go talk to Yu Louchun myself.

38
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:02,810
Wait.

39
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:06,820
Since it's your request, Young Master Fang,

40
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,170
I dare not disobey.

41
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:10,270
I'm the steward of the Girls' Mansion.

42
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:13,100
I hereby make the call to skip today's inspection.

43
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:15,100
I'll report it to Master later.

44
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,070
Yes.

45
00:03:16,210 --> 00:03:16,670
Thank you.

46
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:21,110
I thought the son of the Minister of Revenue

47
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,780
must be a good-for-nothing second generation.

48
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:24,910
I was wrong.

49
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,270
I never liked tea,

50
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:27,870
but there's no wine here.

51
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,140
So I'll drink tea instead of wine,

52
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,040
and propose three toasts to you.

53
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,340
You're welcome, Lu.

54
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:32,870
Save room

55
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,050
for the fine wine of Mountains Red.

56
00:03:35,970 --> 00:03:37,420
The son of Minister of Revenue?

57
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,329
Fang Duobing?

58
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:40,350
Your Highness!

59
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:41,620
Your Highness!

60
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:42,860
Your Highness.

61
00:03:43,329 --> 00:03:44,250
Bad news, Your Highness.

62
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:45,620
[Princess Zhaoyu of Great Xi]

63
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:46,290
The son of Minister of Revenue, Fang Duobing.

64
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,200
The one His Majesty appointed to marry you.

65
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,260
He's gone.

66
00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:50,450
I thought it was a big deal.

67
00:03:50,490 --> 00:03:52,520
But people are saying that he bailed on your marriage.

68
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:55,470
And they say you scared him away because you are eight feet tall,

69
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:57,610
and you have a waist the size of a huge bucket.

70
00:03:57,650 --> 00:03:58,440
What?

71
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,200
He bailed on me?

72
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:02,140
I'm the one who wants to get out of it, okay?

73
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:03,220
By the way,

74
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,790
where did Fang Duobing go?

75
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,870
He seems to have gone to the martial world.

76
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:08,780
Martial world?

77
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:15,100
It's so fun to knock around the martial world.

78
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:19,610
Boss.

79
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:20,820
How much is this?

80
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:22,380
Are you here to have fun yourself, Miss?

81
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,130
Yes.

82
00:04:24,579 --> 00:04:26,660
There's more fun stuff in my warehouse.

83
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:27,790
Do you want to check it out, Miss?

84
00:04:28,089 --> 00:04:28,980
Please. Take me there.

85
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,190
Fang Duobing.

86
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,700
It's all because of you! You had to come to the martial world.

87
00:04:38,030 --> 00:04:40,000
It's because of you that I was abducted here as a servant.

88
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,000
Miss.

89
00:04:51,030 --> 00:04:52,490
You should be more gentle.

90
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,220
If you accidentally break the cup,

91
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:55,620
you'll have your salary deducted again.

92
00:04:57,170 --> 00:04:58,380
Thank you.

93
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,040
You're welcome.

94
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:03,500
Physician Li.

95
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,960
Why are you here so late?

96
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:10,020
It's alright.

97
00:05:10,410 --> 00:05:11,740
Since Physician Li has also arrived,

98
00:05:11,970 --> 00:05:13,730
please come with me to see Master, young masters.

99
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,820
Mountains Red is starting so early?

100
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,380
It'll be a while before the banquet starts.

101
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:20,340
Master wants to see you two alone in advance.

102
00:05:24,650 --> 00:05:27,990
[Jinyu Mansion]

103
00:05:28,370 --> 00:05:28,930
Young masters.

104
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:30,800
Master is inside the Jinyu Mansion.

105
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:32,140
Please go in.

106
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:40,030
The decoration here is different from other places.

107
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,159
Don't you think it's a bit like Yuanbao Villa?

108
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:01,360
Please, make yourselves at home and take a seat.

109
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,800
I'm almost done with this plaything.

110
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:09,700
This is Jade Bone Skill.

111
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,350
You are knowledgeable, Young Master Fang.

112
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:15,220
[Master of Girls' Mansion: Yu Louchun]

113
00:06:12,810 --> 00:06:16,770
You've even heard of this unremarkable life-saving skill of mine.

114
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,730
Jade Bone Skill can make people invincible.

115
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:21,220
It's as powerful as Armor Lock.

116
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,170
Thank you two

117
00:06:30,370 --> 00:06:32,250
for being here at such short notice.

118
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:34,580
I'm very grateful.

119
00:06:35,450 --> 00:06:36,340
Since it's short notice,

120
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,780
there must be something urgent.

121
00:06:39,530 --> 00:06:42,170
I do have a presumptuous request.

122
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:44,740
Young masters, please tell me

123
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:49,140
who killed my best friend, Jin Mantang.

124
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,510
So this is why

125
00:06:54,530 --> 00:06:56,000
you invited us here.

126
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,130
May I ask, Mr. Yu,

127
00:06:58,490 --> 00:06:59,960
were you close to Jin Mantang?

128
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:02,740
I built this Jinyu Mansion

129
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,820
specially for Jin.

130
00:07:05,170 --> 00:07:08,510
I used to invite him here every year for Mountains Red.

131
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:12,400
Jin and I were best friends, and we confided everything to each other.

132
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:13,580
Since the murderer has been arrested,

133
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,900
Mr. Yu, you could have inquired Baichuan Court about it.

134
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:17,190
Why come to us?

135
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,940
Jin was a cautious person.

136
00:07:20,210 --> 00:07:22,140
He wouldn't have been murdered by some greedy unnamable thief.

137
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:25,340
I know there's more to it.

138
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:27,260
You two were there.

139
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:30,170
Could you please tell me what happened exactly?

140
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:32,790
Sorry.

141
00:07:33,570 --> 00:07:35,110
Mr. Yu, there's no need to overthink.

142
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:37,780
There's nothing behind it.

143
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:41,450
You don't believe my friendship with Jin?

144
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,460
It's not that.

145
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,020
Master Yu.

146
00:07:43,409 --> 00:07:44,400
You worry too much.

147
00:07:44,790 --> 00:07:45,590
It's just

148
00:07:45,930 --> 00:07:47,810
when the murderer killed Master Jin,

149
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:50,180
he simply did it for the opal skull.

150
00:07:52,570 --> 00:07:54,690
So I did overthink.

151
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,040
However,

152
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:01,270
something strange happened after the murder.

153
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:04,700
But I don't know if I should tell you about that.

154
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:06,770
What strange thing?

155
00:08:07,050 --> 00:08:07,940
Feel free to tell me.

156
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:11,260
When I was in Yuanbao Villa,

157
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,480
I lost a treasure.

158
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,140
The treasure

159
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:16,530
seems to have been placed together with the opal skull.

160
00:08:16,650 --> 00:08:17,210
Fang Duobing.

161
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:18,070
You saw it too, right?

162
00:08:20,850 --> 00:08:22,600
That treasure is as thin as a cicada's wings,

163
00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:23,740
and it's crystal clear.

164
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,150
It's more like an...

165
00:08:25,570 --> 00:08:26,280
Ice shard?

166
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:29,580
From my point of view,

167
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,800
it's more like a jade bamboo leaf.

168
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:34,200
So you've seen it too, Mr. Yu?

169
00:08:37,490 --> 00:08:39,890
I was just guessing.

170
00:08:40,850 --> 00:08:42,960
Do you know who the treasure thief is?

171
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:44,980
No clue at all.

172
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,460
But Baichuan Court suspects that

173
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,880
Jin Mantang was not from the Central Plains.

174
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,770
We suspect the robber is from another sect.

175
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:53,420
Do you know where he was from, Mr. Yu?

176
00:08:54,460 --> 00:08:56,590
Jin was not from the Central Plains?

177
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:58,980
This is also the first time I've heard about it.

178
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,440
There must be some misunderstanding.

179
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:03,420
I see you have a high-bridged nose

180
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:04,450
and deep eye sockets.

181
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:06,190
I thought you are also a person of mixed blood.

182
00:09:08,170 --> 00:09:10,570
I'm a native of Central Plains.

183
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:12,510
It's getting late.

184
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:15,210
I'm going to make preparations for Mountains Red.

185
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:16,310
Pardon me,

186
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,640
young masters.

187
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,830
Not only does he know about ice shards,

188
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,530
but he also has an ice shard himself.

189
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:38,300
Why don't we visit the Girls' Mansion

190
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,100
in the name of moon-viewing tonight,

191
00:09:39,650 --> 00:09:40,880
and find out where the secret is hidden?

192
00:09:42,970 --> 00:09:53,090
[Jinyu Mansion]

193
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:49,580
Physician Li. Young Master Fang.

194
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,300
The bell of noon has rung.

195
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:53,260
How about I take you back to your rooms for a rest?

196
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,950
The bell doesn't sound close.

197
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,460
You have good hearing, Physician Li.

198
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,160
This is the bell from an ancient temple.

199
00:09:58,420 --> 00:10:00,340
It's about two or three hills away from here.

200
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,100
But

201
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,520
fortunately, it's tranquil around here.

202
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:05,130
We usually arrange our schedule according to the bell.

203
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:08,620
The bells in other temples ring twice, at dawn and dusk.

204
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,530
I've never heard the bell of noon.

205
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:12,500
This temple believes in asceticism.

206
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,950
So, the bell rings three times, at 5 a.m.,

207
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:15,940
noon, and midnight, every day.

208
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:17,540
I won't bother you then, Miss Bihuang.

209
00:10:17,770 --> 00:10:19,630
We'll walk around.

210
00:10:20,170 --> 00:10:20,760
Okay.

211
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:21,260
Okay.

212
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:26,980
You came up from down the mountain.

213
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,650
Have you heard about what happened on Sigu Tea Party?

214
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,470
It's all over the martial world.

215
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:33,450
I didn't expect Li Xiangyi to be such a person.

216
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:35,460
I knew it long ago.

217
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:37,860
I was there

218
00:10:38,010 --> 00:10:39,400
when the incident took place that day.

219
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,950
I happened to be passing by,

220
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:44,180
and I wanted to save Shan Gudao.

221
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,430
But after 100 rounds,

222
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:46,970
I made one tiny mistake,

223
00:10:47,970 --> 00:10:49,490
and Li Xiangyi took the chance

224
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:51,860
to kill Shan Gudao at one swing.

225
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:55,610
So why did he let you go?

226
00:10:57,930 --> 00:10:59,780
I saved Li Xiangyi's life once.

227
00:11:00,450 --> 00:11:02,700
Otherwise, he would have killed me too.

228
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,590
It's said that Mr. Yu invited an extraordinary man.

229
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,700
I didn't expect that

230
00:11:06,810 --> 00:11:08,320
you were invited here

231
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:09,450
because you're good at talking nonsense, Master Dongfang.

232
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:10,410
Fang.

233
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,490
What do you mean?

234
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:12,980
Why don't you go a few rounds with me?

235
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:13,460
Bring it on.

236
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:14,340
I'm not afraid of you.

237
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:15,060
Fang Xiaobao.

238
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:16,100
Calm down.

239
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:16,940
What's the rush?

240
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,900
Maybe Dongfang here

241
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:20,750
really saved Li Xiangyi's life.

242
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:22,610
What are you talking about?

243
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,140
May I ask you, Dongfang,

244
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:27,220
was there any enemy that Li Xiangyi couldn't beat

245
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,630
when he was young?

246
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:31,800
Yes.

247
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:33,740
The thing is

248
00:11:34,180 --> 00:11:35,720
maybe when that enemy

249
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,580
was forcing Li Xiangyi to kneel and beg for mercy,

250
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:39,330
Dongfang here defended the weak

251
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:40,250
and helped Li Xiangyi

252
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:43,160
by kowtowing 18 times instead of him,

253
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,790
and saved his life in the end.

254
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:47,610
Li Lianhua.

255
00:11:48,230 --> 00:11:50,110
You two are ganging up on me.

256
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:51,310
I dare not.

257
00:11:51,350 --> 00:11:52,100
Dongfang.

258
00:11:52,220 --> 00:11:53,220
They were just kidding.

259
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:53,980
Don't take it seriously.

260
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,140
-Yeah. Just kidding./N-Everyone.

261
00:11:56,430 --> 00:11:57,790
Mountains Red is about to start.

262
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,640
Please follow me to Qinhong Hall.

263
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:06,210
[Qinhong Hall]

264
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:13,340
The Mountains Red banquet will be full of beautiful women.

265
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,820
We are lucky today.

266
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:15,620
Shi.

267
00:12:15,860 --> 00:12:17,060
You are a scholar after all.

268
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:18,290
-What?/N-Young Master Fang.

269
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:21,010
It's fun to have beautiful women around while studying.

270
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,280
One side is honor and fame.

271
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,530
The other side is romantic encounters.

272
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:34,450
You are all here.

273
00:12:36,770 --> 00:12:39,570
I admire all of you.

274
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:42,020
It's my honor to have invited all of you here.

275
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:43,270
Everyone,

276
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:45,180
please be seated.

