00:41:07,390 --> 00:41:08,470
The guards couldn't have entered Girls' Mansion

822
00:41:08,500 --> 00:41:09,780
without an order.

823
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:11,950
I also went to bed outside the courtyard at midnight last night.

824
00:41:12,330 --> 00:41:13,130
The guards can testify.

825
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:17,020
So there's no suspect?

826
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:23,050
Young Master Fang.

827
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:26,020
Why did you come to the foot of Kanyun Peak in a hurry last night?

828
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:28,500
Your master abducted and imprisoned commoner girls here.

829
00:41:28,890 --> 00:41:30,850
I was here to interrogate him as Baichuan Court's detective, of course.

830
00:41:31,130 --> 00:41:32,570
But you secretly inquired yesterday

831
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,740
if there are treasures up the mountain.

832
00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:35,980
It's not normal, is it?

833
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:38,150
What about you, Guard Xin?

834
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:40,110
The first thing you checked was the treasure when you rushed in.

835
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:43,870
It doesn't seem normal either, does it?

836
00:41:47,210 --> 00:41:47,760
Guard Xin.

837
00:41:48,270 --> 00:41:49,660
A leg of Master's was found outside.

838
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:50,860
There's a person hidden in the cave of the maple forest.

839
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:51,580
We've blocked him.

840
00:41:52,010 --> 00:41:52,670
Tell the guards

841
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:53,540
to secure the suspension bridge.

842
00:41:53,980 --> 00:41:54,400
Yes.

843
00:41:54,810 --> 00:41:55,990
No one is allowed to leave.

844
00:42:05,910 --> 00:42:07,250
If you don't come out, we'll set fire and smoke you out.

